able stakes — the engines parse schema first, prose second."}],["$","h3",null,{"children":"2. Authorship signals matter again"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"AI engines are calibrated against EEAT-style trust gradients. A human author with a verifiable history weighs more than an SEO content farm. This is the opening for operators with real domain experience."}],["$","h3",null,{"children":"3. Brevity wins citations"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"A clean 40-word answer to a precise question gets quoted. A 2,000-word essay does not. Build for the snippet first, then expand."}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"What we recommend"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Audit your top 50 commercial-intent pages against three structures: schema coverage, author transparency, and quotable passage density. Most B2B sites score under 30%. That's the gap."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-bone/60 italic","children":"— Written by the Cheetah AGI team. If this resonated, the consultation page is below."}]]}]}]}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"section pt-0","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container-tight","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"eyebrow","children":"Keep reading"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl mt-3","children":"More from Field Notes"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3","children":[["$","$L3",null,{"href":"/blog/llm-indexing-content","className":"group block surface hover:border-strike/40 transition-all relative overflow-hidden p-8","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-strike scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 origin-left transition-transform duration-500"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 mb-6 font-mono text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-ink-400","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-strike","children":"GEO / AEO"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"·"}],["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-03-18","children":"Mar 18, 2026"}],["$","